    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Coesio <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Fab</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> Floro <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>rimo</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ilo</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> IV <expan><abbr>Scyt</abbr><ex>hicae</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XI <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audiae</ex></expan> piae fidelis <lb n="6"/>Grania Nigel<lb break="no" n="7"/>la uxor et <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Coe<lb break="no" n="8"/>sius Florus Licin<lb break="no" n="9"/>nianus <note>sic</note> filius </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Γ(αίῳ) Κοισίῳ Γα<lb break="no" n="2"/>ίου υἱῷ Φαβίᾳ Φλώ<lb break="no" n="3"/>ρῳ, πρειμιπιλα<lb break="no" n="4"/>ρίῳ λεγ(ιῶνος) Δ Σκυθι<lb break="no" n="5"/>κῆς, ἐπάρχῳ λεγ(ιῶνος) ΙΑ Κλαυ<lb break="no" n="6"/>δίας εὐσεβοῦς πιστῆς, Γρα<lb break="no" n="7"/>νία Νιγέλλα ἀνδρὶ ἀγα<lb break="no" n="8"/>θῷ καὶ Γ(αίος) Κοίσιος Φλῶρος <lb n="9"/>Λικιννιανὸς ὁ υἱὸς μνή<lb break="no" n="10"/>μης ἕνεκα
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Dem lateinischen folgt der gleichlautende griechische Text. Praef. leg. wohl als praef. (castrorum) leg. aufzufassen. Material: weißer Kalkstein.</p>
